NeSI Web Portal
---------------

Drupal modules developed specifically for use within the NeSI web portal.

:::Requirements:::

 Drupal 7

:::Contrib Modules (available on d.o) :::

 features
 countries
 profile2
 references
 revisioning
 rules
 flag
 views
 nodereference_url
 field_permissions
 eva
 diff
 email_registration

:::Setup Instructions:::

  1. Recommended to install Drush (http://drush.ws/) to ease deployment. 
  2. Install Drupal 7
  3. Install contrib modules
  4. Config - follow as outlined below:


